        "faq_ecCJqT": {
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>You can sign up as a Free Member with as little as your name, email, and address, or join our BEROMASTER tier for a £55 annual membership fee. Visit our Club BERO page to <a href=\"https://berobrewing.com/account/register\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">sign up</span></a>.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_AiHKdt": {
          "settings": {
            "text": "<ul><li>All credits are earned in USD.</li><li>When credits are redeemed, they will be against the current conversion rate.</li><li>By purchasing any BERO 6-pack or Variety Pack online or in-store. Club BERO Free Members receive $0.25 credit for each 6-pack purchased. BEROMASTER members receive double the credit at $0.50 credit for each 6-pack purchase. </li><li>There are other ways to earn credits if you are a Club BERO member—such as referrals, reviews, social follows, and more. Members can see a full list of credit-earning actions in their dashboard.</li></ul>"
          }
        },
