        "faq_cwbHY": {
          "type": "faq",
          "disabled": false,
          "settings": {
            "title": "What rewards can I get?",
            "text": "<ul><li>Rewards depend on your membership tier. For more information on membership tiers and benefits, check out Club BERO <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">here</span>.</li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "faq_NEwExN": {
          "settings": {
            "text": "<ul><li>Here are the steps to redeem your credits:</li><li>Log in to your Club BERO account dashboard <a href=\"/pages/account-club-bero\" title=\"Account Club Bero\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">here</span></a> (you don’t have to be a paid member to redeem credits)</li><li>Click on “redeem credits”</li><li>Enter the amount of credits you want to redeem from your available credit balance</li><li>A unique discount code for that amount will be generated and can be automatically applied to your cart if you choose to do so</li><li>Fill your cart with all your favorite BERO beers and check out with your savings applied</li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "faq_UNKjTf": {
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>If you placed an order on <a href=\"http://www.berobrewing.com\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">www.berobrewing.com</span></a> and:</p><ul><li><strong>Cancel the order</strong> OR <strong>get a full refund for your order</strong>, your Club BERO credits earned for that specific order will no longer be applied to your account. </li><li><strong>Get a partial refund for your order</strong>, only the equivalent Club BERO credits will be deducted from your account.</li></ul><p>Please reach out to our customer service team at <a href=\"mailto:support@berobrewing.com\">support@berobrewing.com</a> if you have any questions. </p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_fdmAqe": {
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>While BEROMASTER memberships are non-refundable—given the immediate value you receive upon purchase—you can cancel at any time by emailing <a href=\"mailto:cancelmembership@berobrewing.com\">cancelmembership@berobrewing.com</a>, so your membership does not renew. Access to your BEROMASTER benefits will remain active until the end of the billing cycle.</p>"
